items.title: Is Novocaine's Disorder Where You Can't Feel Pain Real? What Congenital Insensitivity to Pain Is & How Accurate The Movie Is
items.description: The 2025 action comedy Novocaine begs the question of whether the lead character's condition is a real genetic disorder or a Hollywood plot device.

items.title: Glen Powell To Star In Barry Jenkins’ First Movie After Mufasa: The Lion King
items.description: Glen Powell will join forces with Moonlight and Mufasa: The Lion King's Barry Jenkins in his upcoming sci-fi feature film The Natural Order.
